From Brian Hughes Subject Re Help with SIMM configuration Robert Sprecher writes Can someone please help me understand the current situation regarding SIMMS I can give is a I have a IIsi which I will probably keep for another I would like to add more memory ie go from MB to I know that I will need x or faster Which SIMMS pin or pin You need to get the pin Would the SIMMS I get today be usable in years with a newer more powerful system If you mean in a newer more powerful Mac system then the answer is Apple has stated that all new Macs will use the pin SIMMs and no longer use the pin Hades